snippet.title: The Solitaire Conspiracy - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Solitaire Conspiracy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1424980/The_Solitaire_Conspiracy/



Join a world of near-future spies and take on a supervillain in this supercharged take on classic Solitaire. Precision engineered for replayable espionage action.
